com.mokiat.data.front.parser

Interface IOBJParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OBJParser

    public interface IOBJParser
    The IOBJParser interface provides methods through which users can parse OBJ wavefront resources.
    Author:
    Momchil Atanasov

    • Method Detail

      • setLimits

        void setLimits(OBJLimits limits)
        Sets the limits that need to be followed during parsing.

        If null is specified, then no constraints will be applied.

        Parameters:
        limits - the limits to follow during parsing

      • getLimits

        OBJLimits getLimits()
        Returns the limits that are applied during parsing.

        If null is returned, then no limits have been set.

        Returns:
        an instance of OBJLimits or null if no constraints should be applied.
